### FastAPI 待办事项 API 测试

### 1. 获取根路径
GET http://localhost:8000/
Accept: application/json

### 2. 创建任务
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "编写项目文档",
  "start_time": "2024-01-15T10:00:00",
  "duration_hours": 2.0,
  "due_date": "2024-01-15T14:00:00",
  "priority": 2,
  "depends_on": [],
  "final_deadline": null
}

### 3. 创建另一个任务
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "团队会议",
  "start_time": "2024-01-15T13:00:00",
  "duration_hours": 1.0,
  "due_date": "2024-01-15T15:00:00",
  "priority": 1,
  "depends_on": [],
  "final_deadline": null
}

### 4. 获取所有任务
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/todos
Accept: application/json

### 5. 获取指定任务
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/todos/1
Accept: application/json

### 6. 获取指定日期的任务
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/todos/date/2024-01-15
Accept: application/json

### 7. 获取未来7天的日程安排
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/todos/schedule/days?days=7
Accept: application/json

### 8. 完成任务
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/todos/1/complete
Accept: application/json

### 9. 更新任务
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/todos/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "团队会议（已更新）",
  "priority": 1
}

### 10. 自动重新调度
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/todos/reschedule
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "current_time": "2024-01-15T18:00:00"
}

### 11. 获取日历配置
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/todos/calendar/config
Accept: application/json

### 12. 更新日历配置
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/todos/calendar/config
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "work_days": [0, 1, 2, 3, 4],
  "work_start_hour": 9,
  "work_end_hour": 18,
  "holidays": ["2024-01-01", "2024-02-10"],
  "special_workdays": ["2024-01-28"]
}

### 13. 删除任务
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/v1/todos/1
Accept: application/json

